&lt;li&gt;Maintains tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applies films and decals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sandblasts, preps, sands, tapes, paints, and decals heavy equipment, trucks, and trailers&lt;/li&gt;
