&lt;li&gt;Checks and maintains inventory of paint and supplies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performs housekeeping on assigned work areas, during and at completion of work. Removes scrap and performs general cleaning and sweeping.&lt;/li&gt;
